```plantuml
@startuml Fintan-contents_case-studies
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor Developer

rectangle "Frontend" as FE {
  rectangle "React App" as ReactApp #lightblue
  rectangle "Redux" as Redux #lightgoldenrodyellow
}

rectangle "Backend Services" as BE {
  rectangle "Spring Boot API" as SpringAPI #lightcoral
  rectangle "gRPC Service" as gRPCService #lightgreen
  rectangle "Message Queue\n(ZeroMQ)" as MessageQueue #wheat
}

rectangle "CI/CD Pipeline" as CICD #lightgray {
  rectangle "Azure DevOps" as AzureDevOps
  rectangle "CircleCI" as CircleCI
  rectangle "AWS CodeBuild" as AWSCodeBuild
}

rectangle "Monitoring & Logging" as Monitoring #lightyellow {
  rectangle "New Relic" as NewRelic
  rectangle "Elastic Stack" as ElasticStack
}

rectangle "Authentication & Authorization" as Auth #lightpink {
  rectangle "Spring Security" as SpringSecurity
  rectangle "Facebook OAuth" as FacebookOAuth
}

' ========= Connections =========
Developer --> FE : develop features
Developer --> BE : implement APIs

ReactApp <--> Redux : state management
ReactApp --> SpringAPI : HTTP requests
SpringAPI <--> gRPCService : gRPC communication
gRPCService --> MessageQueue : push notifications

CICD --> ReactApp : build & deploy
CICD --> SpringAPI : build & deploy
CICD --> gRPCService : build & deploy

SpringAPI --> Monitoring : log data
gRPCService --> Monitoring : log data
Monitoring --> NewRelic : performance data
Monitoring --> ElasticStack : log aggregation

SpringAPI --> Auth : secure endpoints
Auth <--> SpringSecurity : session management
Auth <--> FacebookOAuth : social login

@enduml
```